WEBVTT

00:00:00.872 --> 00:00:04.709
If you identify
as a person with disability,

00:00:05.793 --> 00:00:07.503
kindly close your eyes,

00:00:08.671 --> 00:00:10.548
and in your head, repeat after me:

00:00:11.758 --> 00:00:14.302
I am a person

00:00:15.344 --> 00:00:16.637
with disability.

00:00:20.433 --> 00:00:21.601
Thank you.

00:00:23.936 --> 00:00:26.189
I have bipolar disorder, type two.

00:00:27.774 --> 00:00:29.817
I am brave to say it now,

00:00:29.859 --> 00:00:34.572
but it actually took me almost 20 years
to be clinically diagnosed.